==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hastener
<hw>Has"ten*er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who hastens.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which hastens; especially, a stand or reflector
used for confining the heat of the fire to meat while roasting before
it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hastif</ent>⟦br⟧
